{"kanda":6,"sarga":94,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"स प्रविश्यसभांराजादीनःपरमदुःखितः ।निषपादासनेमुख्येसिंहःक्रुद्धइवश्वसन्","trans":"Ravana, the king entered the council, angry like a lion, looking piteous, very sad and sat on the seat.","words":[{"d":"दीनः","m":"piteous"},{"d":"परमदुःखितः","m":"very sad"},{"d":"सःराजा","m":"that king"},{"d":"सभाम्","m":"council"},{"d":"प्रविश्य","m":"entered"},{"d":"क्रुद्धः","m":"angry"},{"d":"सिंहःइव","m":"like lion"},{"d":"श्वसन्","m":"sighing"},{"d":"मुख्ये","m":"chief"},{"d":"आसने","m":"seat"},{"d":"निषसाद","m":"sat"}]},{"v":2,"dev":"अब्रवीच्च स तान्सर्वान् बलमुख्यान् महाबलः ।रावणःप्राञ्जलिर्वाक्यंपुत्रव्यसनकर्शितः","trans":"Ravana, endowed with mighty prowess, shrunken on account of his son, greeting all the army chiefs with folded hands spoke as follows.","words":[{"d":"महाबलः","m":"endowed with mighty prowess"},{"d":"पुत्रव्यसनकर्शितः","m":"shrunken on account of son"},{"d":"सःरावणः","m":"that Ravana"},{"d":"प्राञ्जलिः","m":"greeting with folded hands"},{"d":"तान्","m":"them"},{"d":"सर्वान्","m":"all"},{"d":"बलमुख्यान्","m":"army chiefs"},{"d":"वाक्यम्","m":"words"},{"d":"अब्रवीच्छ","m":"spoke"}]},{"v":3,"dev":"सर्वेभवन्तस्सर्वेणहस्त्यश्वेनसमावृताः ।निर्यान्तुरथसङ्घैश्चपादातैश्चोपशोभिताः","trans":"","words":[{"d":"सर्वे","m":"all"},{"d":"भवन्तः","m":"of you"},{"d":"सर्वेण","m":"all"},{"d":"हस्त्वश्वेन","m":"elephants horses"},{"d":"समावृताः","m":"collected"},{"d":"रथसङ्घैश्च","m":"also chariots"},{"d":"पादातैश्च","m":"foot soldiers too"},{"d":"उपशोभिताः","m":"shining"},{"d":"निर्यान्तु","m":"march"}]},{"v":4,"dev":"एकंरामंपरिक्षिप्यसमरेहन्तुमर्हथ ।वर्षन्तश्शरवर्षाणिप्रावृट् कालइवाम्बुदाः","trans":"","words":[{"d":"एकम्","m":"one"},{"d":"रामम्","m":"Rama"},{"d":"परिक्षिप्य","m":"encompassing"},{"d":"समरे","m":"in war"},{"d":"प्रावृटकाले","m":"monsoon"},{"d":"अम्बुदाःइव","m":"like the sky"},{"d":"शरवर्षाणि","m":"rain of arrows"},{"d":"वर्षन्तः","m":"raining"},{"d":"हन्तुम्","m":"kill"},{"d":"अर्हथ","m":"ought to do"}]},{"v":5,"dev":"अथवाहंशरैस्तीक्ष्णैर्भिन्नगात्रंमहाहवे ।भवद्भिःश्वोनिहन्तास्मिरामंलोकस्यपश्यतः","trans":"\"I shall kill him with huge sharp arrows as the world looks at Rama, once his limbs are struck by you.\"","words":[{"d":"अथवा","m":"or else"},{"d":"अहम्","m":"I"},{"d":"महाहवे","m":"huge"},{"d":"तीक्ष्णैः","m":"sharp"},{"d":"शरैः","m":"arrows"},{"d":"भवद्भि: भिन्नगात्रम्","m":"limbs are struck by you"},{"d":"रामम्","m":"Rama"},{"d":"लोकस्य","m":"world"},{"d":"पश्यतः","m":"looks at"},{"d":"श्वः","m":"I"},{"d":"निहन्तास्मि","m":"I shall kill"}]},{"v":6,"dev":"इत्येतद्वाक्यमादायरक्षसेन्द्रस्यराक्षसाः ।निर्ययुस्तेरथैःशीघ्रैर्नानानीकैश्चसंयुताः","trans":"On Rakshasa king speaking like that, all the diverse battalions together departed swiftly on chariots.","words":[{"d":"ते","m":"they"},{"d":"राक्षसाः","m":"Rakshasa"},{"d":"राक्षसेन्द्रस्य","m":"Rakshasa king's"},{"d":"इति","m":"thus"},{"d":"एतत्","m":"all that"},{"d":"वाक्यम्","m":"words"},{"d":"आदाय","m":"hearing"},{"d":"शीघ्रैः","m":"swiftly"},{"d":"रथैः","m":"on chariots"},{"d":"नानानीकैश्च","m":"diverse battalions"},{"d":"संयुताः","m":"together"},{"d":"निर्ययुः","m":"departed"}]},{"v":7,"dev":"परिघान् पट्टसांश्चैवशरखङ्गपरश्वधान् ।शरीरान्तकरान् सर्वेचिक्षिपुर्वानरान् प्रति वानराश्चद्रुमान्शैलान्राक्षसान्प्रतिचिक्षिपुः ।","trans":"All the Rakshasas threw at the Vanaras iron bars, clubs, axes, swords, and arrows, which were capable of destroying the life. Vanaras also attacked Rakshasas with trees and rocks.","words":[{"d":"सर्वे","m":"all"},{"d":"शरीरान्तकरान्","m":"capable of destroying the life of body"},{"d":"परिघान्","m":"iron bars"},{"d":"पट्टसांश्चव","m":"clubs"},{"d":"शरखङ्गपरश्वधान्","m":"arrows. swords and axes"},{"d":"वानरान् प्रति","m":"on Vanaras"},{"d":"चिक्षिपुः","m":"hurled"},{"d":"वानराश्च","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"राक्षसान् प्रति","m":"over Rakshasas"},{"d":"द्रुमान्","m":"trees"},{"d":"शैलान्","m":"rocks"},{"d":"चिक्षिपुः","m":"attacked"}]},{"v":8,"dev":"स सङ्ग्रामोमहाभीमस्सूर्यस्यदयनंप्रति रक्षसांवानराणां च तुमुलस्समपद्यत ।","trans":"By the time of sunrise, the most terrific war started between Vanaras and Rakshasas, which became tumultuous.","words":[{"d":"सूर्यस्य","m":"Sun"},{"d":"उदयनंप्रति","m":"started at rise"},{"d":"रक्षसाम्","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"वानराणां च","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"महाभीमः","m":"most terrific"},{"d":"सःसङ्ग्रामः","m":"war"},{"d":"तुमुलः","m":"tumultuous"},{"d":"समपद्यत","m":"became"}]},{"v":9,"dev":"तेगदाभिश्चचित्राभिःप्रासैःखडगैःपरश्वधैः अन्योन्यंसमरेजघ्नुस्तदावानरराक्षसाः ।","trans":"The Vanaras and Rakshasas attacked one another with wonderful maces, darts, swords, and axes in war.","words":[{"d":"ते","m":"they"},{"d":"वानरराक्षसाः","m":"Vanaras and Rakshasas"},{"d":"तदा","m":"then"},{"d":"चित्राभिः","m":"wonderful"},{"d":"गदाभिः","m":"maces"},{"d":"प्रासैः","m":"darts"},{"d":"खडगैः","m":"swords"},{"d":"परश्वधैः","m":"axes"},{"d":"समरे","m":"in war"},{"d":"अन्योन्यम्","m":"one another"},{"d":"जघ्नुः","m":"attacked"}]},{"v":10,"dev":"एवंप्रवृत्तेसङ्ग्रामेह्यद्भुतंसुमहद्रजः रक्षसांवानराणां च शान्तंशोणितविस्रवैः ।","trans":"As the war was in progress, wonderful dust had risen which subsided by the flow of blood of Vanaras and Rakshasas.","words":[{"d":"एवम्","m":"in that manner"},{"d":"सङ्ग्रामे","m":"in war"},{"d":"प्रवृत्ते","m":"in progress"},{"d":"अद्भुतम्","m":"wonderful"},{"d":"सुमहत्","m":"huge"},{"d":"रक्षसाम्","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"वानराणां च","m":"Vanaras also"},{"d":"शोणितविस्रवैः","m":"by the flow of blood"},{"d":"शान्तम्","m":"subsided"}]},{"v":11,"dev":"मातङ्गरथकूलाश्चवाजिमत्सास्यध्वजद्रुमाः शरीरसङ्घाटवहाःप्रसस्रुःशोणितापगाः ।","trans":"There with rivers of blood flowing, elephants and chariots were like banks, horses were like fish, staff of chariots like trees and dead bodies as logs of wood seemed.","words":[{"d":"मातङ्गरथकूलाः","m":"elephants and chariots as banks"},{"d":"वाजिमत्स्याः","m":"horses like fish"},{"d":"ध्वजद्रुमाः","m":"staffs as trees"},{"d":"शरीरसङ्घाटवहाः","m":"dead bodies as logs of wood"},{"d":"शोणितापगाः","m":"rivers of blood"},{"d":"प्रसस्रुः","m":"flowed"}]},{"v":12,"dev":"ततस्तेवानराःसर्वेशोणितौघपरिप्लुताः ध्वजवर्मरथानश्वान्नानाप्रहरणानि च ।आप्लुत्याप्लुत्यसमरेवानरेन्द्राबभञ्चिरे","trans":"Leaping and jumping the Vanaras and also the leaders of Vanaras bathed in blood broke all kinds of weapons, staff of chariots and the horses.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"सर्वे","m":"all"},{"d":"ते","m":"of them"},{"d":"वानराः","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"शोणितौघपरिप्लुताः","m":"bathed in blood"},{"d":"समरे","m":"in war"},{"d":"वानरेन्द्राः","m":"leaders of Vanaras"},{"d":"ध्वजवर्मरथान्","m":"staff of chariots"},{"d":"अश्वान्","m":"horses"},{"d":"नानाप्रहरणानि च","m":"all kinds of weapons"},{"d":"आप्लुत्य","m":"leaping"},{"d":"आप्लुत्य","m":"and jumping"},{"d":"बभञ्जिरे","m":"broke"}]},{"v":13,"dev":"ततस्तेवानराःसर्वेशोणितौघपरिप्लुताः ध्वजवर्मरथानश्वान्नानाप्रहरणानि च ।आप्लुत्याप्लुत्यसमरेवानरेन्द्राबभञ्चिरे","trans":"Leaping and jumping the Vanaras and also the leaders of Vanaras bathed in blood broke all kinds of weapons, staff of chariots and the horses.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"सर्वे","m":"all"},{"d":"ते","m":"of them"},{"d":"वानराः","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"शोणितौघपरिप्लुताः","m":"bathed in blood"},{"d":"समरे","m":"in war"},{"d":"वानरेन्द्राः","m":"leaders of Vanaras"},{"d":"ध्वजवर्मरथान्","m":"staff of chariots"},{"d":"अश्वान्","m":"horses"},{"d":"नानाप्रहरणानि च","m":"all kinds of weapons"},{"d":"आप्लुत्य","m":"leaping"},{"d":"आप्लुत्य","m":"and jumping"},{"d":"बभञ्जिरे","m":"broke"}]},{"v":14,"dev":"केशान् कर्णललाटं च नासिकाश्चप्लवङ्गमाः ।रक्षसांदशनैस्तीक्ष्णैर्नखैश्चापिव्यकर्तयन्","trans":"The monkeys with their sharp teeth and nails tore off the hair, ears, noses, and forehead of the Rakshasas,","words":[{"d":"प्लवङ्गमाः","m":"monkeys"},{"d":"तीक्ष्णैः","m":"sharp"},{"d":"दशनैः","m":"teeth"},{"d":"नखैश्चापि","m":"nails"},{"d":"रक्षसाम्","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"केशान्","m":"hair"},{"d":"कर्णललाटांश्च","m":"ears, forehead"},{"d":"नासिकाश्चापि","m":"noses"},{"d":"व्यकर्तयन्","m":"tore off"}]},{"v":15,"dev":"एकैकंराक्षसंसङ्ख्येशतंवानरपुङ्गवाः ।अभ्यधावन्तफलिनंवृक्षंशकुनयोयथा","trans":"Just as trees laden with fruits are attacked by birds, each one of the Rakshasas was attacked by hundreds of Vanaras.","words":[{"d":"सङ्ख्ये","m":"number of"},{"d":"एकैकम्","m":"each one"},{"d":"राक्षसम्","m":"of the Rakshasas"},{"d":"शतम्","m":"hundred"},{"d":"वानरपुङ्गवाः","m":"Vanara leaders"},{"d":"फलिनम्","m":"laden with fruits"},{"d":"वृक्षम्","m":"trees"},{"d":"शकुनयोयथा","m":"like birds"},{"d":"अभ्यधावन्त","m":"attacked"}]},{"v":16,"dev":"तदागदाभिर्गुर्वीभिःप्रासैःखडगैःपरश्वधैः ।निर्जघ्नुर्वानरान्घोरान्राक्षसाःपर्वतोपमाः","trans":"Then the mountainlike forms of Rakshasas attacked the Vanaras with heavy maces, darts, swords, and axes in frightening ways.","words":[{"d":"तदा","m":"then"},{"d":"पर्वतोपमाः","m":"mountain like forms"},{"d":"राक्षसाः","m":"Rakshasa"},{"d":"गुर्वीभिः","m":"heavy"},{"d":"गदाभिः","m":"maces"},{"d":"प्रासैःखडगैः","m":"darts, swords"},{"d":"परश्वधैः","m":"axes"},{"d":"वानरान्","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"निर्जघ्नुः","m":"struck"}]},{"v":17,"dev":"राक्षसैर्वध्यमानानांवानराणांमहाचमूः ।शरण्यंशरणंयातारामंदशरथात्मजम्","trans":"The Vanaras being struck by Rakshasas sought the protection of Rama, the son of Dasharatha.","words":[{"d":"राक्षसैः","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"वध्यमानानाम्","m":"being struck"},{"d":"वानराणाम्","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"महाचमूः","m":"huge group"},{"d":"शरण्यम्","m":"refuge"},{"d":"दशरथात्मजम्","m":"Dasharatha's son"},{"d":"रामम्","m":"Rama"},{"d":"शरणम्","m":"protection"},{"d":"याता","m":"sought"}]},{"v":18,"dev":"ततोरामोमहातेजाधनुरादायवीर्यवान् ।प्रविश्यराक्षसंसैन्यंशरवर्षंववर्ष ह","trans":"Then, the highly energetic and valiant Rama, taking up the bow showered rain of arrows on Rakshasa army.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"महातेजाः","m":"highly energetic"},{"d":"वीर्यवान्","m":"valiant one"},{"d":"रामः","m":"Rama"},{"d":"धनुः","m":"bow"},{"d":"आदाय","m":"taking up"},{"d":"राक्षसम्","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"सैन्यम्","m":"army"},{"d":"शरवर्षम्","m":"rain of arrows"},{"d":"ववर्ष ह","m":"showered"}]},{"v":19,"dev":"प्रविष्टंतुतदारामंमेघास्सूर्यमिवाम्बरे ।नाथिजग्मुर्महाघोरानिर्दहन्तंशराग्निना","trans":"Then Rama entered the army with fire like arrows which were consuming the Rakshasas like the clouds in the sky which can't approach the scorching Sun.","words":[{"d":"तदा","m":"then"},{"d":"प्रविष्टम्","m":"entered"},{"d":"शराग्निना","m":"like fire of arrows"},{"d":"निर्दहन्तम्","m":"consuming"},{"d":"रामम्","m":"Rama"},{"d":"महाघोराः","m":"most dreadful"},{"d":"अम्बरे","m":"sky"},{"d":"मेघाः","m":"clouds"},{"d":"सूर्यमिव","m":"like sun"}]},{"v":20,"dev":"कृतान्येवसुघोराणिरामेणरजनीचराः ।ददृशुस्ते न वैरामंकर्माण्यसुकराणिते","trans":"The night rangers were able to see Rama's terrible action which was difficult for others only after he had performed not otherwise (as they could not see his quick movement).","words":[{"d":"ते","m":"those"},{"d":"रजनीचराः","m":"night rangers"},{"d":"रणे","m":"in war"},{"d":"रामेण","m":"by Rama"},{"d":"कृतानि","m":"deeds"},{"d":"सुघोराणि","m":"terrible"},{"d":"असुकराणि","m":"difficult for others"},{"d":"रामस्य","m":"Rama's"},{"d":"कर्माण्येव","m":"his action"},{"d":"ददृशुः","m":"could not see"}]},{"v":21,"dev":"चालयन्तंमहासैन्यंविधमन्तंमहारथान् ।ददृशुस्ते न वैरामंवातंवनगतंयथा","trans":"They could not see Rama while he was moving and breaking huge chariots as one would not be able to see the trees in the forest when the wind blew fast.","words":[{"d":"ते","m":"those"},{"d":"महासैन्यम्","m":"great army"},{"d":"चालयन्तम्","m":"moving"},{"d":"महारथान्","m":"huge chariots"},{"d":"विधमन्तम्","m":"breaking"},{"d":"रामम्","m":"Rama"},{"d":"वनगतम्","m":"blowing in the forest"},{"d":"वातंयथा","m":"wind like"},{"d":"न ददृशुः","m":"not see"}]},{"v":22,"dev":"छिन्नंभिन्नंशरैर्दग्धंप्रभन्नंशस्त्रपीडितम् ।बलंरामेणददृशुर्नरामंशीघ्रकारिणम्","trans":"They saw the army shattered, broken into pieces, tormented with darts by Rama but could not make out Rama who was very fast in action.","words":[{"d":"रामेण","m":"by Rama"},{"d":"शरैः","m":"arrows"},{"d":"छिन्नम्","m":"shattered"},{"d":"शस्त्रपीडितम्","m":"tormented with darts"},{"d":"बलम्","m":"army"},{"d":"शीघ्रकारिणम्","m":"one who is very fast in action"},{"d":"रामम्","m":"Rama"},{"d":"न","m":"not make out"}]},{"v":23,"dev":"प्रहरन्तंशरीरेषु न तेपश्यन्तिराघवम् ।इन्द्रियार्थेषुतिष्ठन्तंभूतात्मानमिवप्रजाः","trans":"Just as created beings experience their senses and do not perceive their soul, the army experienced the hitting of Raghava by their senses but were not able to perceive him who was hitting them.","words":[{"d":"शरीरेषु","m":"in the body"},{"d":"प्रहरन्तम्","m":"hitting"},{"d":"राघवम्","m":"Raghava"},{"d":"ते","m":"they"},{"d":"इन्द्रियार्थेषु","m":"experienced through sense objects"},{"d":"तिष्ठन्तम्","m":"enjoying"},{"d":"भूतात्मानम्","m":"created beings"},{"d":"प्रजाःइव","m":"like people"},{"d":"न पश्यन्ति","m":"not able to perceive"}]},{"v":24,"dev":"एषहन्तिगजानीकमेषहन्तिमहारथान् ।एषहन्तिशरैस्तीक्ष्णैःपदातीस्वाजिभिःसह इतितेराक्षसास्सर्वेरामस्यसदृशान्रणे ।अन्योन्यंकुपिताजघ्नुस्सादृश्याद्राघवस्यते","trans":"'Rama is here killing elephants', 'Here is Rama destroying chariot warriors', 'Rama is killing horses, foot soldiers with sharp arrows', saying like that, the Rakshasas were striking one another in the battle. Being there where Rama was, they were mistaking one another for Rama there because of the socalled resemblance and attacking one another.","words":[{"d":"एषः","m":"in that way"},{"d":"गजानीकम्","m":"elephants"},{"d":"एषः","m":"in the same way"},{"d":"महारथान्","m":"mighty chariot warriors"},{"d":"हन्ति","m":"destroying"},{"d":"एषः","m":"so also"},{"d":"तीक्ष्णैः","m":"sharp"},{"d":"शरैः","m":"arrows"},{"d":"वाजिभिःसह","m":"including horses"},{"d":"पदातीन्","m":"foot soldiers"},{"d":"हन्ति","m":"killing"},{"d":"इति","m":"thus"},{"d":"सर्वे","m":"all"},{"d":"तेराक्षसाः","m":"those"},{"d":"रणे","m":"in battle"},{"d":"रामस्य","m":"Rama's"},{"d