a alone at another place","words":[{"d":"रणे","m":"in war"},{"d":"तेराक्षसाः","m":"those Rakshasas"},{"d":"रामसहस्राणि","m":"thousand Ramas"},{"d":"पश्यन्ति","m":"saw"},{"d":"महाहवे","m":"great battle"},{"d":"पुनः","m":"again"},{"d":"एकम्","m":"one"},{"d":"काकुत्स्थमेव","m":"kakuthsa alone"},{"d":"पश्यन्ति","m":"could see"}]},{"v":28,"dev":"भ्रमन्तीकाञ्चनींकोटिंकार्मुकस्यमहात्मनः ।अलातचक्रप्रतिमांददृशुस्ते न राघवम्","trans":"While Rama was going around in circles with his bow, the Rakshasas were confused, and saw the golden ends of the bow to be like a burning fire stick circling and could not see Rama.","words":[{"d":"ते","m":"they"},{"d":"महात्मनः","m":"great soul"},{"d":"कार्मुकस्य","m":"bow's"},{"d":"भ्रमन्ती","m":"confusion"},{"d":"काञ्चनीम्","m":"golden"},{"d":"अलातचक्रप्रतिमाम्","m":"going round in circles"},{"d":"कोटिम्","m":"burning firestick"},{"d":"ददृशुः","m":"saw"},{"d":"राघवम्","m":"Raghava"},{"d":"न","m":"not"}]},{"v":29,"dev":"शरीरनाभिसत्त्वार्चिश्शरारंनेमिकार्मुकम् ।ज्याघोषतलनिर्घोषंतेजोबुधदिगुणप्रभम् दिव्यास्त्रगुणपर्यन्तंनिघ्नन्तंयुधिराक्षसान् ।ददृशूरामचक्रंतत्कालचक्रमिवप्रजाः","trans":"People saw Rama in the form of wheel exterminating the Rakshasas on the battlefield, which had the body of Sri Rama as its navel, his strength as its glow, the arrows as spokes, his bow as belly, the twangling of the bowstring as its sound, his virtues and effulgence as the power of his mystic missiles in war. Rama was seen as a wheel of time spirit by the people.","words":[{"d":"प्रजाः","m":"people"},{"d":"शरीरनाभिः","m":"body as centre of discuss"},{"d":"सत्त्वार्चिः","m":"strength as glow"},{"d":"शरारम्","m":"arrows as spokes"},{"d":"नेमिकार्मुकम्","m":"bow for belly"},{"d":"ज्याघोषतलनिर्घोषम्","m":"twangling of the bow string"},{"d":"तेजोबुधदिगुणप्रभम्","m":"virtues and effulgence as power of missiles"},{"d":"दिव्यास्त्रगुणपर्यन्तम्","m":"power of mystic missiles"},{"d":"युधि","m":"in war"},{"d":"राक्षसान्","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"निघ्नन्तम्","m":"killing"},{"d"